===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{context|nonce}} A [[disease]] of the lungs, caused by inhaling [[mineral]] or [[metallic]] dust, such as [[silicon]] and [[quartzite]].  The silicates then lacerate the lining of the lungs, causing the victim to leak air from their lungs while simultaneously bleeding into their lung cavity.

